    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-out-single-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ふ～……やっとお腹が落ち着いてきましたわ\n風が気持ちいいですわね",
      "startTime": 5.6865868568,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "……どうしてでしょう。あれだけ焼肉を食べたのに\n胸のもやもやがいまだに消えませんわ",
      "startTime": 12.4311139385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "それなら、この感覚は一体……？",
      "startTime": 16,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "……はっ！　い、いえ、今のはなんでも……！",
      "startTime": 20.2333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "すず、どうしたんだ？",
      "startTime": 24.5,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "……なんでもないですわ",
      "startTime": 27.2,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "なんでもないことはないだろう\nトリビュートライブからずっと様子が変だぞ？",
      "startTime": 31.3145578384,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "き、気付いていたんですの！？",
      "startTime": 34.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "当たり前だ。俺はすずのマネージャーなんだからな\n何か悩みがあるのなら、なんでも言ってくれ",
      "startTime": 41.7840763684,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "……ええっと、その……",
      "startTime": 44.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "い、以前、星見プロのメンバーの中で\n話題になったことがありますの……",
      "startTime": 51.6680663209,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは……\n気になっている人はいませんの？",
      "startTime": 56.5131693314,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、ち、違うんですのよ！？\nみんなで話すうちにそういう話になったんですの！",
      "startTime": 61.8527199253,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "ほ、ほら、星見プロのメンバーにはそういう話を\nポップにする人がいるでしょう！？",
      "startTime": 68.626410046,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "渚とか、芽衣とか、優とか……！",
      "startTime": 71.3666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "落ち着いてくれ。今は星見プロのみんなのことで\n頭が一杯だよ。もちろんすずのことも大事に思ってる",
      "startTime": 78.1114810958,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "そう……ですの",
      "startTime": 82.9666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "……ところで{user}さん\n今、私達は夜の浜辺を二人きりで歩いている訳ですが",
      "startTime": 89.4963390317,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "この状況に……ドキドキしたりしませんこと？",
      "startTime": 96.3051239014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "ドキドキ……か？　あ、いや、俺としては\n久しぶりにすずとゆっくり話せて単純に嬉しいけど",
      "startTime": 105.1979760329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz016.m4a",
      "text": "……はぁ～",
      "startTime": 109.6051239014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz017.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さんは相変わらずですわね\n私ばかりそわそわして……なんだかバカみたいですわ",
      "startTime": 115.2933701697,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz018.m4a",
      "text": "やっぱり私の勘違いだったのかもしれないですわね",
      "startTime": 120.4017567952,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz019.m4a",
      "text": "まさかトリビュートライブの時と\n同じ勘違いをするなんて……",
      "startTime": 128.5304966122,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz020.m4a",
      "text": "でも、{user}さんが星見プロのみんなを\nどれだけ想っているか、改めて聞けたのは嬉しいですわ",
      "startTime": 134.2923867181,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "急にすっきりした顔になったな\n悩みは解決した……のか？",
      "startTime": 142.6638446318,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz021.m4a",
      "text": "そういうことにしておきますわ",
      "startTime": 146.0350901286,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 5507.714436800001,
          "startTime": 151.5428045654
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz022.m4a",
      "text": "さあ、もう少し歩きましょう？",
      "startTime": 148.3350901286,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-coast-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 4668.7744157,
          "startTime": 153.0038645443
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz023.m4a",
      "text": "この砂浜を\nよくみんなで走ったことを思い出しますわ",
      "startTime": 155.8317626754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz024.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣が朝から元気一杯で\nあのテンションについていくのも大変でしたわね",
      "startTime": 161.9093906902,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz025.m4a",
      "text": "それと、リズノワの前で砂浜の話をしたら、莉央さんが\n「下半身強化にちょうどいいわね」と言い出しましたの",
      "startTime": 171.4463128298,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz026.m4a",
      "text": "その場で遠征トレーニングの予定を組み始めて\nこころにとてつもなく恨めしそうに睨まれましたわ……",
      "startTime": 179.938055139,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "莉央さんはストイックだからな\n今回の練習でも頼りになっただろ？",
      "startTime": 187.7195777574,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz027.m4a",
      "text": "そうですわね\nさすが麻奈様とライバル関係にあっただけありますわ",
      "startTime": 192.6603273246,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-suz028.m4a",
      "text": "{user}さん\nこの場所に、麻奈様との思い出はありますの？",
      "startTime": 198.4765029204,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03/sud_vo_adv_card_suz_04_03-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈とはよく一緒に散歩してたよ\n「ここだと思いきり歌えるから」って、よく歌ってたな",
      "startTime": 205.678694717,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_coast-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 152.7565877278
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
